<font color=#FFFF00>Hati-hati, anak-anak.</font>

28
00:01:21,651 --> 00:01:22,921
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai nanti./
Sampai nanti.</font>

29
00:01:22,921 --> 00:01:24,892
<font color=#FFFF00>Hati-hati.</font>

30
00:01:25,061 --> 00:01:27,692
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai nanti.</font>

31
00:01:28,632 --> 00:01:31,032
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan khawatir.</font>

32
