33
00:01:41,942 --> 00:01:43,681
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo, Guru.</font>

34
00:01:44,981 --> 00:01:46,041
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo.</font>

35
00:01:46,681 --> 00:01:47,681
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo.</font>

36
00:01:47,912 --> 00:01:50,621
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian sudah disini?</font>

37
00:01:51,022 --> 00:01:53,522
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami di sini untuk memeriksa anak-anak.</font>

38
00:01:53,522 --> 00:01:56,252
<font color=#FFFF00>Tetaplah disini jika sudah selesai.</font>

39
00:01:56,492 --> 00:01:59,392
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka banyak menangkap kerang kemarin.</font>

40
00:02:00,061 --> 00:02:01,061
<font color=#FFFF00>Begitukah?</font>

41
00:02:02,261 --> 00:02:04,201
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya...</font>

42
00:02:04,602 --> 00:02:07,701
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita punya dokter baru
di rumah sakit kapal.</font>

43
00:02:08,032 --> 00:02:09,502
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan halo.</font>

44
00:02:09,502 --> 00:02:10,741
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo./
Bagus.</font>

45
00:02:10,741 --> 00:02:11,771
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo.</font>

46
00:02:11,771 --> 00:02:14,472
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini Dokter Song Eun Jae ahli bedah./
Halo</font>

47
00:02:15,342 --> 00:02:17,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku Cha Joon Young, dokter gigi./
Halo.</font>

48
00:02:17,182 --> 00:02:20,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan.../
Penyakit Dalam, Kwak Hyun.</font>

49
00:02:22,581 --> 00:02:23,782
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kau...</font>

50
00:02:23,882 --> 00:02:24,951
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau baik-baik saja?</font>

51
00:02:25,551 --> 00:02:28,821
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau tidak datang mengunjungiku?</font>

52
00:02:29,222 --> 00:02:30,222
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

53
00:02:30,962 --> 00:02:32,692
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kalian sudah kenal?</font>

54
00:02:32,891 --> 00:02:34,831
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia anak sahabatku.</font>

55
00:02:34,831 --> 00:02:38,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu Kwak Sung...</font>

56
00:02:38,562 --> 00:02:41,602
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Kwak Sung. Dia besar di sini.</font>

57
00:02:43,402 --> 00:02:44,472
<font color=#FFFF00>Kwak Sung?</font>

58
00:02:44,972 --> 00:02:46,972
<font color=#FFFF00>Dulu dia ahli bedah di sini.</font>

59
00:02:47,312 --> 00:02:49,942
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa Ayahmu masih
tidak mau kembali ke Korea?</font>

60
00:02:51,081 --> 00:02:53,041
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya. Masih.</font>

61
00:02:53,182 --> 00:02:56,652
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia harus melakukannya dengan baik
diusianya sekarang.</font>

62
00:02:58,282 --> 00:03:00,192
<font color=#FFFF00>Mari kita masuk.</font>

63
00:03:00,821 --> 00:03:02,222
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikutlah bersama kami.</font>

64
00:03:02,222 --> 00:03:05,122
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo./
Ayo masuk.</font>

65
00:03:05,122 --> 00:03:07,291
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan lari./
Tidak.</font>

66
00:03:07,632 --> 00:03:08,692
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aigoo.</i></font>

67
00:03:08,692 --> 00:03:10,402
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Selanjutnya.</i></font>

68
00:03:10,402 --> 00:03:12,002
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak sakit sama sekali.</font>

69
00:03:12,002 --> 00:03:13,062
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh?/
Iya.</font>

70
00:03:18,201 --> 00:03:21,011
<font color=#FFFF00>136 cm, 44 kg.</font>

71
00:03:21,011 --> 00:03:22,872
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tadi sarapan pagi?</font>

72
00:03:22,872 --> 00:03:25,741
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus berbagi.</font>

73
00:03:26,412 --> 00:03:27,782
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa pekerjaan Ayahmu?</font>

74
00:03:29,782 --> 00:03:30,821
<font color=#FFFF00>Buka lebar.</font>

75
00:03:31,981 --> 00:03:33,521
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[SD Somang]</i></font>

76
00:03:40,231 --> 00:03:41,231
<font color=#FFFF00>Sakit?</font>

77
00:03:48,602 --> 00:03:50,502
<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah selesai.</font>

78
00:03:50,502 --> 00:03:52,171
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sehat.</font>

79
00:03:52,171 --> 00:03:54,241
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengarkan Gurumu, mengerti?</font>

80
00:03:54,342 --> 00:03:55,342
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak baik.</font>

81
00:03:55,771 --> 00:03:58,882
<font color=#FFFF00>Giliranmu. Siapa namamu?</font>

82
00:03:59,182 --> 00:04:01,852
<font color=#FFFF00>Kim Jin Woo./
Jin Woo, di mana sakitnya?</font>

83
00:04:02,182 --> 00:04:03,252
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak baik.</font>

84
00:04:03,821 --> 00:04:06,622
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan memeriksa paru-parumu.
Tarik nafas dalam-dalam.</font>

85
00:04:07,222 --> 00:04:08,491
<font color=#FFFF00>Buang.</font>

86
00:04:09,652 --> 00:04:10,692
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Kim.</font>

87
00:04:11,291 --> 00:04:13,962
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau kesepian karena yang lain
pergi ke sekolah?</font>

88
00:04:14,092 --> 00:04:15,132
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

89
00:04:16,762 --> 00:04:18,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Kopimu sangat harum.</font>

90
00:04:18,702 --> 00:04:19,731
<font color=#FFFF00>Benarkah?</font>

91
00:04:21,871 --> 00:04:24,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Reaksi macam apa itu?</font>

92
00:04:25,202 --> 00:04:28,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Seharusnya kau bilang, "Kau mau secangkir teh?"</font>

93
00:04:28,012 --> 00:04:30,012
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau mungkin juga, "Apa aku harus buatkan untukmu?"</font>

94
00:04:30,642 --> 00:04:32,912
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah itu yang biasa dikatakan orang normal?</font>

95
00:04:33,652 --> 00:04:36,311
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku heran bagaimana
kau akan bisa berkencan dengan wanita di klub.</font>

96
00:04:37,251 --> 00:04:39,352
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus bertindak seperti di klub
ketika di tempat kerja?</font>

97
00:04:41,191 --> 00:04:43,121
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau agak aneh hari ini.</font>

98
00:04:46,092 --> 00:04:47,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

99
00:04:47,462 --> 00:04:49,662
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia menyindirku?</font>

100
00:04:51,332 --> 00:04:53,871
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, tidak./
Benarkah?</font>

101
00:04:54,532 --> 00:04:56,501
<font color=#FFFF00>Kedengarannya dia tidak ingin...</font>

102
00:04:56,501 --> 00:04:59,371
<font color=#FFFF00>...mendengar omelan wanita tua,
jadi kau harus berhenti.</font>

103
00:04:59,371 --> 00:05:00,912
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapten.</font>

104
00:05:16,722 --> 00:05:17,892
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo?</font>

105
00:05:19,592 --> 00:05:20,631
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

106
00:05:21,731 --> 00:05:22,892
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa?</font>

107
00:05:25,361 --> 00:05:27,501
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak akan mengobatiku?</font>

108
00:05:27,602 --> 00:05:29,871
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukannya tidak mau.
Aku tidak bisa.</font>

109
00:05:30,142 --> 00:05:32,272
<font color=#FFFF00>{\an8}Pengerasan pada hati sehingga
sel-sel hati akan kehilangan fungsinya.</font>

110
00:05:30,142 --> 00:05:32,272
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami tidak bisa menyembuhkan
<i>sirosis hati.</i></font>

111
00:05:32,772 --> 00:05:34,712
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak ingin sembuh total.</font>

112
00:05:35,111 --> 00:05:37,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bahkan tidak ingin hidup lebih lama.</font>

113
00:05:38,681 --> 00:05:42,311
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya ingin bertahan satu bulan lagi.</font>

114
00:05:43,412 --> 00:05:46,722
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau tidak meminta bantuan roh?</font>

115
00:05:49,551 --> 00:05:50,691
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, kau.</font>

116
00:05:50,991 --> 00:05:53,892
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang mengikutimu itu?</font>

117
00:05:53,892 --> 00:05:56,491
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia terlihat sangat mirip denganmu.</font>

118
00:05:57,731 --> 00:05:59,462
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memakai baju biru...</font>

119
00:05:59,462 --> 00:06:01,702
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan punya luka di dahinya.</font>

120
00:06:05,041 --> 00:06:07,311
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau tahu kakakku
punya luka di dahinya?</font>

121
00:06:07,712 --> 00:06:10,541
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tepat berdiri di sebelahmu.</font>

122
00:06:11,481 --> 00:06:13,811
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada sesuatu yang ingin ia katakan.</font>

123
00:06:17,051 --> 00:06:20,852
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan membantuku?</font>

124
00:06:32,532 --> 00:06:33,801
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lapar.</font>

125
00:06:35,631 --> 00:06:39,501
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo makan. Aku menghangatkan sup.</font>

126
00:06:39,501 --> 00:06:42,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Banyak yang kalian urus?
Kalian terlambat makan siang.</font>

127
00:06:42,012 --> 00:06:44,741
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah makan?/
Iya. Makanlah.</font>

128
00:06:44,741 --> 00:06:46,241
<font color=#FFFF00>Perawat Pyo.</font>

129
00:06:46,241 --> 00:06:50,251
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa peramal menelpon seseorang
di kapal ini?</font>

130
00:06:50,251 --> 00:06:52,421
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa? Tentu saja.</font>

131
00:06:52,852 --> 00:06:54,152
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia menelponnya?</font>

132
00:06:54,152 --> 00:06:56,722
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Pengobatan Korea langsung pergi tadi.</font>

133
00:06:57,022 --> 00:06:59,892
<font color=#FFFF00>Jae Geol?/
Brengsek itu? Untuk apa?</font>

134
00:06:59,892 --> 00:07:03,162
<font color=#FFFF00>Untuk apa lagi selain mengobatinya?</font>

135
00:07:04,131 --> 00:07:06,431
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia membawa jarum dan obat.</font>

136
00:07:08,972 --> 00:07:11,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian kemana? Kalian harus makan.</font>

137
00:07:11,142 --> 00:07:13,811
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menghangat supnya untuk kalian.</font>

138
00:07:32,592 --> 00:07:34,032
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

139
00:07:34,491 --> 00:07:36,361
<font color=#FFFF00>Jauhi pasienku.</font>

140
00:07:36,361 --> 00:07:38,962
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa pasienmu?</font>

141
00:07:40,671 --> 00:07:43,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau lihat itu? Dia memilihku.</font>

142
00:07:43,402 --> 00:07:45,001
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi kau akan memberinya obat ini?</font>

143
00:07:45,501 --> 00:07:48,012
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu betapa berbahayanya
penderita sirosis hati ini?</font>

144
00:07:48,012 --> 00:07:50,412
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada banyak makalah tentang hati.</font>

145
00:07:50,412 --> 00:07:52,441
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Kim./
Tentu saja,</font>

146
00:07:52,881 --> 00:07:54,981
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tidak akan langsung
memberinya obat.</font>

147
00:07:55,282 --> 00:07:57,722
<font color=#FFFF00>Pertama, aku akan mengobati mualnya dengan
akupuntur.</font>

148
00:07:58,282 --> 00:08:00,392
<font color=#FFFF00>{\an8}Peradangan pada hati atau liver.</font>

149
00:07:58,282 --> 00:08:00,392
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasien sirosis hati
rentan terkena <i>hepatitis</i>.</font>

150
00:08:00,392 --> 00:08:02,251
<font color=#FFFF00>Melakukan akupunktur di tempat terbuka...</font>

151
00:08:02,251 --> 00:08:04,991
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir aku tidak akan melakukan
tindakan pencegahan pada infeksi?</font>

152
00:08:05,522 --> 00:08:08,092
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasien sirosis hati mudah mengalami pendarahan.</font>

153
00:08:08,092 --> 00:08:10,032
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang kau khawatirkan?</font>

154
00:08:10,561 --> 00:08:12,801
<font color=#FFFF00>Jarumnya hanya berdiameter 0.2 mm,</font>

155
00:08:12,801 --> 00:08:15,801
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan aku memasukkannya ke dalam
kapiler <i>(pembuluh darah terkecil)</i> diameter 0,01 mm.</font>

156
00:08:15,801 --> 00:08:17,202
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tidak akan menyebabkan pendarahan.</font>

157
00:08:17,202 --> 00:08:20,241
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebar vena <i>(pembuluh balik)</i> tidak menentukan
apa pendarahannya berhenti.</font>

158
00:08:20,241 --> 00:08:22,541
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tergantung apa
pasien memiliki faktor pembekuan darah.</font>

159
00:08:22,541 --> 00:08:25,741
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian bisa berhenti?
Aku merasa pusing.</font>

160
00:08:27,512 --> 00:08:30,082
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang diinginkan pasien saat ini
bukanlah obat.</font>

161
00:08:30,082 --> 00:08:32,121
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini adalah elevasi
dari gejala-gejalanya.</font>

162
00:08:32,121 --> 00:08:34,822
<font color=#FFFF00>Mual adalah kondisi
terburuknya saat ini.</font>

163
00:08:34,822 --> 00:08:37,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi, kau akan melanjutkan pengobatan
akupuntur yang tidak ilmiah itu?</font>

164
00:08:37,661 --> 00:08:38,922
<font color=#FFFF00>"Tidak ilmiah"?</font>

165
00:08:38,922 --> 00:08:42,092
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau menyebut sesuatu yang tidak
kau mengerti dengan tidak ilmiah?</font>

166
00:08:42,092 --> 00:08:43,702
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan perawatannya.</font>

167
00:08:43,702 --> 00:08:45,531
<font color=#FFFF00>Omong kosong.</font>

168
00:08:46,062 --> 00:08:47,531
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter Kwak./
Kwak.</font>

169
00:08:49,172 --> 00:08:51,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana menurutmu?/
Bagaimana menurutmu?</font>

170
00:08:58,082 --> 00:09:00,712
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harap pasien
segera sembuh.</font>

171
00:09:02,011 --> 00:09:03,822
<font color=#FFFF00>Lebih dari itu,</font>

172
00:09:03,822 --> 00:09:07,891
<font color=#FFFF00>...dua dokter yang berkelahi
di depan pasien,</font>

173
00:09:07,891 --> 00:09:11,062
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak akan memperbaik kondisinya.</font>

174
00:09:11,292 --> 00:09:14,661
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya. Aku setuju dengan dia.</font>

175
00:09:15,231 --> 00:09:18,102
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah kalian bertiga.</font>

176
00:09:18,102 --> 00:09:20,401
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah kau menyuruh mereka saja
dan aku tetap disini?</font>

177
00:09:21,972 --> 00:09:23,401
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku membawa ini.</font>

178
00:09:23,401 --> 00:09:25,401
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, aku harus disini.</font>

179
00:09:25,401 --> 00:09:28,212
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus mengeluarkan jarum dan
menyelesaikan pembicaraan kita.</font>

180
00:09:28,212 --> 00:09:30,712
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah menyuruh kalian pergi.</font>

181
00:09:31,511 --> 00:09:35,011
<font color=#FFFF00>Berada di sekitar kalian akan
membuatku tambah sakit.</font>

182
00:09:35,781 --> 00:09:37,052
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi pergilah.</font>

183
00:09:37,322 --> 00:09:40,082
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergi dari sini sekarang.</font>

184
